@startuml
actor Consumer
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant Database as DB
participant "Payment Gateway" as Payment
actor Vendor

Consumer -> App: Browse available food
App -> DB: Request food items near location
DB --> App: Return food list
App --> Consumer: Display food items

Consumer -> App: Select food item
Consumer -> App: Enter quantity
App --> Consumer: Show total price

Consumer -> App: Click "Order"
App -> Payment: Process payment
Payment --> App: Payment successful
App -> DB: Create order record
DB --> App: Order saved

App -> Vendor: Send order notification
App --> Consumer: Order confirmation

Vendor -> App: Mark order as ready
App --> Consumer: Notification: Order ready for pickup

Consumer -> Vendor: Pickup food
Vendor --> Consumer: Hand over food

@enduml